104
00:05:08,039 --> 00:05:09,631
Listen to me, you're the one I'm with.

105
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:10,829
You knowl love you.

106
00:05:11,039 --> 00:05:13,473
So will you please relax
because you're driving me crazy.

107
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:17,072
ltjust comes flying out of her mouth.

108
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:20,789
She doesn't know that she said it. And
it's a little bit of an elephant in the room.

109
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,916
But it's wonderful. I think she's always--

110
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:26,311
-She's always known that she loves him.
-Yes, she just hasn't said the word.

111
00:05:26,479 --> 00:05:27,753
