of a commitment-phobe.

112
00:05:27,919 --> 00:05:30,069
Remember first time you said it,
she said, "Thank you."

113
00:05:30,239 --> 00:05:31,718
Right. Oh, I remember.

114
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,399
-That was a rough one.
-Mm-hm.

115
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,630
And you kept coming back.

116
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:37,592
Leonard's a fighter.

117
00:05:37,759 --> 00:05:40,193
-He's a fighter, man.
-He doesn't give up.

118
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,713
