-All right.

132
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,477
We just were totally
in Leonard and Penny world.

133
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:26,869
l was no one else but her at that moment.
It was strange.

134
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:30,077
It did. It felt like we were the only
two people in the room. That's exactly--

135
00:06:30,239 --> 00:06:31,752
That's what you strive for on stage.

136
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:34,758
But especially with all of this,
all this technical--

137
00:06:34,919 --> 00:06:37,717
I mean, 500 people in the room,
it's really hard to achieve that.

138
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:41,031
So, yeah, we did it once
and never looked back.

139
00:06:41,479 --> 00:06:42,468
I love you.

140
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,428
I love you too.

141
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:47,998
