-Oh, I would die.

156
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,068
[LAUGHS]

157
00:07:36,599 --> 00:07:38,954
You don't know what it's like
to feel completely frustrated.

158
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:40,956
To have a desire build up within you...

159
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:44,435
...and then be denied any opportunity
for release.

