176
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:38,679
It's not this, it's this,
with these little things in there.

177
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:41,029
And that's been great, though...

178
00:08:41,239 --> 00:08:43,514
...because those are movements
that are more true to life.

179
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:46,280
-They feel huge.
