communicates and works things out...

217
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:47,393
...but it works for them
and they're both honest with each other.

218
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:50,797
It's, I guess, the basis
of a good long-term relationship, right?

219
00:10:50,999 --> 00:10:52,557
