224
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,834
Are you ever gonna sleep with Amy?

225
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:07,157
All right, we're down the rabbit hole.
What are you doing?

226
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,993
I don't know another relationship
that's been this long-term, stable...

227
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,752
...and intimate
without being consummated.

228
00:11:12,959 --> 00:11:15,234
-I think it's really kind of sweet and amazing.
PARSONS Yeah.

229
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:19,069
And it's not the focal point of our plot lines
or of our relationship.

230
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:21,635
